{"tid":903914,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[幾時到支支]美國經濟制裁十七名沙特人","createTime":"2018-11-16T02:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T03:24:55.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"927a6c3c5267139bd235f42802c7281752663201","tid":903914,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國宣布對十七名涉及卡舒吉案的沙特阿拉伯人實施經濟制裁。<br />\n<br />\n國務院發言人諾爾特在記者會上表示，財政部決定經濟制裁十七名相信有份參與殺害卡舒吉的沙特人，當中包括與沙特王儲關係密切的官員。<br />\n<br />\n諾爾特指他們的行為違反人權，必須為此負上責任。<br />\n<br />\n華府會凍結他們在美國的資產，禁止他們與美國的公司及個人進行交易。美國早前已宣布對他們實施旅遊禁令，限制他們入境美國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=327449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D327449&d=cVkKFaQom%2Bj3qDTSP7JoTf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c822bf2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D327449&h=67fc0f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=327449</a>"},{"pid":"c13e39da7a7a3cc77c5927cbf0b0a67d7351c021","tid":903914,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eb92644088c8b81a29e73df06cf7d38f5c1cf2","tid":903914,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"制裁成個新疆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1a5a41c894ecaa83ed26b5fdef9f7431c7a020","tid":903914,"uid":11258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:24:55.000Z","msg":"沙特王儲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}